<div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
  <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">Section 14: Services Catalogue</h2>

  <p class="mb-6 text-white/70">
    All microservices in the Meridian Console platform. Each service is independently deployable and
    owns its own database schema.
  </p>

  <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
    <div class="scope-panel">
      <h4 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-indigo-400">Gateway</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">
        YARP-based reverse proxy. Single public entry point for all API traffic.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="scope-panel">
      <h4 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-indigo-400">Identity</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">
        Authentication, authorization, user/org management, JWT tokens.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="scope-panel">
      <h4 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-indigo-400">Servers</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">
        Game server lifecycle: create, start, stop, configure, delete.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="scope-panel">
      <h4 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-indigo-400">Nodes</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">Agent inventory, health monitoring, capacity management.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="scope-panel">
      <h4 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-indigo-400">Tasks</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">Background jobs, scheduled operations, orchestration.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="scope-panel">
      <h4 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-indigo-400">Files</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">File metadata, S3 upload/download orchestration, backups.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="scope-panel">
      <h4 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-indigo-400">Mods</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">Mod registry, versioning, installation management.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="scope-panel">
      <h4 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-indigo-400">Console</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">Real-time console streaming via SignalR.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="scope-panel">
      <h4 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-indigo-400">Billing</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">Subscriptions, usage metering, payment processing.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="scope-panel">
      <h4 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-indigo-400">Notifications</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">Email, Discord, webhook delivery.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="scope-panel">
      <h4 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-indigo-400">Firewall</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">UniFi integration, port management.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="scope-panel">
      <h4 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-indigo-400">Secrets</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">Credential storage, rotation management.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="scope-panel">
      <h4 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-indigo-400">Discord</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">Bot integration for server events and commands.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
